OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with rain.
OL,6,FDrier and eventually clearer weather
OL,7,Fwith the odd shower will spread south
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon. Fresh
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly winds veering northerly
OL,10,Fand easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FChance of a few showers this
OL,13,Fevening. Then the rest of the night
OL,14,Fwill be dry and cold with clear
OL,15,Fperiods and a slight frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FMost of the day will be dry
OL,18,Fwith some hazy sunshine in the
OL,19,Fmorning. Outbreaks of rain will spread
OL,20,Feast in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
