OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FAny
OL,6,Fovernight rain clearing Friday morning
OL,7,Fto leave just a few showers. Bright
OL,8,Fwith occasional showers Saturday, rain
OL,9,Flater. Windy with showers or longer
OL,10,Fspells of rain on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
